    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Tarlith Vhal Sereth — Senior Partner, Cindren &amp; Vhal Rel Astra</h2>\n<p><em>The named villain of Phase 4. The conspiracy's most senior visible operator. Indictable, removable, or killable; not the conspiracy itself.</em></p>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>Late fifties. Tall, narrow-shouldered, very thin. Dark Aerdi complexion, hair gone silver-white and worn long, tied back. Clipped silver beard. Dark eyes that miss nothing. Dark-grey Aerdi advocate's overcoat. Heavy seal-ring on his right hand bearing the firm's seal, not a personal device. Smiles only with his mouth.</p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>Not a combatant.</strong> Sereth has no significant combat training. He carries a hand crossbow and a concealed dagger as a senior commercial officer's standard precaution; he has used neither in twenty years. <strong>His protection is his guards.</strong> Two Bodyguards (Veteran), one Bodyguard Captain (Knight, Defense fighting style) at his offices; one Bodyguard outside the offices; a Driver (Bandit Captain) at his carriage. He yields if isolated and reduced to half HP.</p>\n<p>His one rule: <strong>he does not personally kill.</strong> Has not in twenty years and will not now.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 5, PB +3)</h3>\n<p><strong>AC</strong> 13 (fine wool coat over hidden mail) · <strong>HP</strong> 65 (10d8+20) · <strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft. · <strong>Init</strong> +1 · <strong>Passive Perception</strong> 14</p>\n<p><strong>STR</strong> 10 (+0) · <strong>DEX</strong> 12 (+1) · <strong>CON</strong> 14 (+2) · <strong>INT</strong> 18 (+4) · <strong>WIS</strong> 14 (+2) · <strong>CHA</strong> 16 (+3)</p>\n<p><strong>Saves:</strong> INT +7, WIS +5, CHA +6.</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Deception +6, History +7, Insight +5, Investigation +7, Persuasion +6.</p>\n<p><strong>Senses:</strong> Passive Perception 14. <strong>Languages:</strong> Common, Old Aerdi, Suloise, Aerdi imperial cipher.</p>\n<h3>Traits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cunning Action.</strong> Bonus action to Disengage or Hide.</li>\n<li><strong>Reader of Rooms.</strong> Advantage on Insight and Investigation checks against any creature whose intentions he has read for at least one round.</li>\n<li><strong>The Senior Partner's Guard.</strong> Always accompanied at his offices by Two Bodyguards (Veteran) and a Bodyguard Captain (Knight, Defense). Outside, by one Bodyguard. In his carriage, by a Driver (Bandit Captain).</li>\n<li><strong>Yields.</strong> Surrenders and offers terms if reduced to half HP and not within reach of his guards. Never makes a killing blow himself.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Actions</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hand Crossbow (last resort).</strong> Ranged Weapon Attack +4, range 30/120. <em>Hit:</em> 1d6+1 piercing.</li>\n<li><strong>Concealed Dagger (last resort).</strong> Melee Weapon Attack +4, reach 5 ft. <em>Hit:</em> 1d4+1 piercing.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 4.</em> See <em>Rel Astra NPCs → Tarlith Vhal Sereth</em> and <em>The Sereth Confrontation</em> for the scene's full setup.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
